${images.map((img, idx) => `Image ${idx + 1}${img.pageNumber ? ` (Page ${img.pageNumber})` : ''}: ${img.imageUrl}`).join('\n')}

**REQUIRED: Every flashcard MUST include an imageUrl field.**

